<plot>The Tecate SCORE Baja 1000 is one of the greatest thrills in auto racing. "Drive Like Hell" is a 90-minute feature documentary that captures this free-wheeling desert race like never before. Filmed in high definition television, "Drive Like Hell" takes a first-ever, behind-the-scenes look at the 1000.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?160242</url></doc>
